# Infrastructure — Terraform + AWS

3-hesap izolasyonu (dev / staging / prod). AWS eu-central-1. Terraform ile reusable module pattern.

## Dizin Yapısı

```
infrastructure/terraform/
├── modules/                  # Reusable modules
│   ├── network/             # VPC, subnets, NAT gateway
│   ├── database/            # Aurora PostgreSQL
│   ├── cache/               # ElastiCache Redis
│   ├── ecs-service/         # ECS Fargate service template
│   ├── alb/                 # Application Load Balancer
│   ├── s3-bucket/           # S3 with encryption + lifecycle
│   ├── secrets/             # Secrets Manager
│   └── cloudfront/          # CDN + WAF
└── environments/
    ├── dev/
    │   ├── main.tf          # Compose modules
    │   ├── variables.tf
    │   ├── terraform.tfvars
    │   └── backend.tf       # S3 state
    ├── staging/
    └── prod/
```

## Terraform Backend — S3 + DynamoDB

Her environment kendi state bucket:

```hcl
# environments/prod/backend.tf
terraform {
  backend "s3" {
    bucket         = "leanmgmt-terraform-state-prod"
    key            = "prod/terraform.tfstate"
    region         = "eu-central-1"
    encrypt        = true
    dynamodb_table = "leanmgmt-terraform-locks-prod"
    kms_key_id     = "alias/terraform-state-key"
  }
}
```

State bucket'lar versioning + encryption + MFA delete (prod).

## Module Pattern

Her module `main.tf`, `variables.tf`, `outputs.tf`, `versions.tf`:

```hcl
# modules/database/variables.tf
variable "environment" {
  type        = string
  description = "dev | staging | prod"
  validation {
    condition     = contains(["dev", "staging", "prod"], var.environment)
    error_message = "environment dev, staging veya prod olmalı"
  }
}

variable "vpc_id" { type = string }
variable "private_subnet_ids" { type = list(string) }

variable "instance_class" {
  type    = string
  default = "db.r6g.large"
}

variable "backup_retention_days" {
  type    = number
  default = 7
  validation {
    condition     = var.backup_retention_days >= 7
    error_message = "Backup retention minimum 7 gün"
  }
}

variable "deletion_protection" {
  type    = bool
  default = true
}
```

```hcl
# modules/database/main.tf
resource "aws_rds_cluster" "aurora_postgres" {
  cluster_identifier      = "leanmgmt-${var.environment}-aurora"
  engine                  = "aurora-postgresql"
  engine_version          = "16.1"
  database_name           = "leanmgmt"
  master_username         = "leanmgmt_admin"
  manage_master_user_password = true  # Secrets Manager rotation

  db_subnet_group_name    = aws_db_subnet_group.main.name
  vpc_security_group_ids  = [aws_security_group.db.id]

  backup_retention_period = var.backup_retention_days
  preferred_backup_window = "02:00-03:00"
  preferred_maintenance_window = "sun:03:00-sun:05:00"

  storage_encrypted       = true
  kms_key_id              = aws_kms_key.db.arn

  deletion_protection     = var.deletion_protection
  skip_final_snapshot     = var.environment != "prod"
  final_snapshot_identifier = var.environment == "prod" ? 
    "leanmgmt-prod-final-${formatdate("YYYY-MM-DD", timestamp())}" : null

  enabled_cloudwatch_logs_exports = ["postgresql"]

  tags = local.common_tags
}

resource "aws_rds_cluster_instance" "main" {
  count                = var.environment == "prod" ? 2 : 1  # prod multi-AZ
  cluster_identifier   = aws_rds_cluster.aurora_postgres.id
  instance_class       = var.instance_class
  engine               = aws_rds_cluster.aurora_postgres.engine
  engine_version       = aws_rds_cluster.aurora_postgres.engine_version
  performance_insights_enabled = true
  
  tags = local.common_tags
}
```

```hcl
# modules/database/outputs.tf
output "cluster_endpoint" {
  value = aws_rds_cluster.aurora_postgres.endpoint
}

output "reader_endpoint" {
  value = aws_rds_cluster.aurora_postgres.reader_endpoint
}

output "master_secret_arn" {
  value = aws_rds_cluster.aurora_postgres.master_user_secret[0].secret_arn
}
```

## Environment Composition

```hcl
# environments/prod/main.tf
module "network" {
  source      = "../../modules/network"
  environment = "prod"
  cidr_block  = "10.0.0.0/16"
  az_count    = 3
}

module "database" {
  source                = "../../modules/database"
  environment           = "prod"
  vpc_id                = module.network.vpc_id
  private_subnet_ids    = module.network.private_subnet_ids
  instance_class        = "db.r6g.xlarge"
  backup_retention_days = 14
  deletion_protection   = true
}

module "cache" {
  source             = "../../modules/cache"
  environment        = "prod"
  vpc_id             = module.network.vpc_id
  private_subnet_ids = module.network.private_subnet_ids
  node_type          = "cache.r6g.large"
  num_cache_nodes    = 2
}

module "api_service" {
  source           = "../../modules/ecs-service"
  environment      = "prod"
  service_name     = "api"
  task_cpu         = 1024
  task_memory      = 2048
  desired_count    = 3
  container_image  = "${aws_ecr_repository.api.repository_url}:${var.api_image_tag}"
  
  environment_vars = {
    NODE_ENV     = "production"
    DATABASE_URL = "postgresql://..."  # read from secrets in task def
  }
  
  secrets = {
    JWT_ACCESS_SECRET_CURRENT = aws_secretsmanager_secret.jwt_access.arn
  }
}
```

## Resource Naming

Konvensiyon: `leanmgmt-<env>-<service>-<detail>`

| Resource | Örnek |
|---|---|
| VPC | `leanmgmt-prod-vpc` |
| Aurora cluster | `leanmgmt-prod-aurora` |
| ElastiCache | `leanmgmt-prod-redis` |
| ECS cluster | `leanmgmt-prod-cluster` |
| ECS service | `leanmgmt-prod-api` |
| ALB | `leanmgmt-prod-alb` |
| S3 bucket | `leanmgmt-prod-documents-<random>` (global unique) |
| Secrets | `leanmgmt-prod/jwt-access-secret-current` |

## Common Tags

```hcl
# environments/*/locals.tf
locals {
  common_tags = {
    Environment = var.environment
    Project     = "lean-management"
    ManagedBy   = "terraform"
    Owner       = "platform-team"
  }
}
```

Her resource'a `tags = local.common_tags` (merged with resource-specific tags).

Cost allocation + governance için zorunlu.

## Least-Privilege IAM

ECS task role:

```hcl
resource "aws_iam_role" "ecs_task" {
  name = "leanmgmt-${var.environment}-ecs-task-role"

  assume_role_policy = jsonencode({
    Version = "2012-10-17"
    Statement = [{
      Effect = "Allow"
      Principal = { Service = "ecs-tasks.amazonaws.com" }
      Action = "sts:AssumeRole"
    }]
  })
}

resource "aws_iam_role_policy" "ecs_task_policy" {
  role = aws_iam_role.ecs_task.id
  
  policy = jsonencode({
    Version = "2012-10-17"
    Statement = [
      # Secrets Manager — sadece gerekli secret'lar
      {
        Effect = "Allow"
        Action = ["secretsmanager:GetSecretValue"]
        Resource = [
          aws_secretsmanager_secret.jwt_access.arn,
          aws_secretsmanager_secret.jwt_refresh.arn,
          aws_secretsmanager_secret.db_master.arn,
        ]
      },
      # S3 — sadece documents bucket
      {
        Effect = "Allow"
        Action = ["s3:GetObject", "s3:PutObject", "s3:DeleteObject"]
        Resource = ["${aws_s3_bucket.documents.arn}/*"]
      },
      # CloudWatch Logs
      {
        Effect = "Allow"
        Action = ["logs:CreateLogStream", "logs:PutLogEvents"]
        Resource = "${aws_cloudwatch_log_group.api.arn}:*"
      },
    ]
  })
}
```

Wildcard resource (`"Resource": "*"`) **yasak** — specific ARN listele.

## Security Group Pattern

Layered security groups:

```hcl
# ALB: public HTTPS
resource "aws_security_group" "alb" {
  name        = "leanmgmt-${var.environment}-alb"
  description = "ALB public HTTPS ingress"
  vpc_id      = var.vpc_id

  ingress {
    from_port   = 443
    to_port     = 443
    protocol    = "tcp"
    cidr_blocks = ["0.0.0.0/0"]
  }

  egress {
    from_port = 0
    to_port   = 0
    protocol  = "-1"
    cidr_blocks = ["0.0.0.0/0"]
  }
}

# ECS: only from ALB
resource "aws_security_group" "ecs" {
  name   = "leanmgmt-${var.environment}-ecs"
  vpc_id = var.vpc_id

  ingress {
    from_port       = 3001
    to_port         = 3001
    protocol        = "tcp"
    security_groups = [aws_security_group.alb.id]
  }

  egress {
    from_port   = 0
    to_port     = 0
    protocol    = "-1"
    cidr_blocks = ["0.0.0.0/0"]
  }
}

# DB: only from ECS
resource "aws_security_group" "database" {
  name   = "leanmgmt-${var.environment}-database"
  vpc_id = var.vpc_id

  ingress {
    from_port       = 5432
    to_port         = 5432
    protocol        = "tcp"
    security_groups = [aws_security_group.ecs.id]
  }
  # No egress
}
```

"Allow from anywhere" yok. Her SG explicit source.

## Secrets — Secrets Manager + Rotation

```hcl
resource "aws_secretsmanager_secret" "jwt_access" {
  name        = "leanmgmt-${var.environment}/jwt-access-secret-current"
  description = "JWT access token signing secret"
  kms_key_id  = aws_kms_key.secrets.arn
  
  tags = local.common_tags
}

resource "aws_secretsmanager_secret_rotation" "jwt_access" {
  secret_id           = aws_secretsmanager_secret.jwt_access.id
  rotation_lambda_arn = aws_lambda_function.jwt_rotator.arn

  rotation_rules {
    automatically_after_days = 180
  }
}
```

Plaintext secret asla Terraform'da. `aws_secretsmanager_secret_version.initial_value` deploy sonrası console'dan set.

## 3-Hesap İzolasyonu

Her environment ayrı AWS hesap:
- **Dev hesabı** — developer erişimi, non-prod data
- **Staging hesabı** — production-like, QA + test verileri
- **Prod hesabı** — minimal erişim, real data, ağır approval gate

Hesaplar arası cross-account role (deployment için):

```hcl
# Staging hesabında — deploy role prod'a access
resource "aws_iam_role" "prod_deployer" {
  name = "leanmgmt-prod-deployer"

  assume_role_policy = jsonencode({
    Version = "2012-10-17"
    Statement = [{
      Effect = "Allow"
      Principal = {
        AWS = "arn:aws:iam::${var.staging_account_id}:role/github-actions-oidc"
      }
      Action = "sts:AssumeRole"
      Condition = {
        StringEquals = {
          "sts:ExternalId" = var.deploy_external_id
        }
      }
    }]
  })
}
```

Staging → Prod deploy belgelenmiş external ID ile.

## GitHub Actions OIDC

Long-lived AWS credentials YASAK. GitHub OIDC ile short-lived:

```hcl
resource "aws_iam_openid_connect_provider" "github_actions" {
  url             = "https://token.actions.githubusercontent.com"
  client_id_list  = ["sts.amazonaws.com"]
  thumbprint_list = ["6938fd4d98bab03faadb97b34396831e3780aea1"]
}

resource "aws_iam_role" "github_deployer" {
  name = "leanmgmt-${var.environment}-github-deployer"

  assume_role_policy = jsonencode({
    Version = "2012-10-17"
    Statement = [{
      Effect = "Allow"
      Principal = {
        Federated = aws_iam_openid_connect_provider.github_actions.arn
      }
      Action = "sts:AssumeRoleWithWebIdentity"
      Condition = {
        StringEquals = {
          "token.actions.githubusercontent.com:aud" = "sts.amazonaws.com"
        }
        StringLike = {
          "token.actions.githubusercontent.com:sub" = 
            "repo:leanmgmt/platform:ref:refs/heads/main"
        }
      }
    }]
  })
}
```

## State Management

- **Never commit `.tfstate`** (`.gitignore`)
- State backup otomatik (S3 versioning)
- State locking DynamoDB (concurrent apply engellenir)
- `terraform plan` her PR'da CI'da — diff review
- `terraform apply` sadece main merge sonrası

## Banned Patterns

- Hardcoded `AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID` / `AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY` (OIDC kullan)
- `"*"` IAM resource (specific ARN)
- `0.0.0.0/0` SG ingress (load balancer dışında)
- `skip_final_snapshot = true` prod'da
- `deletion_protection = false` prod DB'de
- State local (`backend "local"` yasak prod'da)
- Module'e dışarıdan resource passing yerine variable (clear contract)
- Inline policy JSON copy-paste (module + data source)
- Cross-account root access (dedicated role kullan)

